Version 0.2.0
==============
  * Changed the directory and file names  so that they follow the standard naming convention.
  * Added support to handle ligatures, such as "ksha", followed by a vowel sign.
  * Cleaned up the sintex.lex a bit.
  * Corrected few mistakes in the example.pdf.
  * Anuradha Ratnaweera <anuradha@taprobane.org> debianized the Version 0.1.0 and this version is also debianized based on that initial debianization.

Version 0.1.0
===============
Initial version (released as Version 0.01)
